<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://lithub.com/james-patterson-remembers-the-time-james-baldwin-fought-norman-mailer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">James Patterson Remembers the Time James Baldwin Fought Norman Mailer</a></strong><br />
<em>“They were arguing loudly, fists clenched, looking like they were ready to rumble.”</em><br />
By James Patterson</h4>
<p>My first New York literary party taught me that, like a lot of secret societies, the inner world of literary people was borderline crazy and completely overrated.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://lithub.com/james-patterson-remembers-the-time-james-baldwin-fought-norman-mailer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>[Keep reading&#8230;]</em></a></p>
<span class="caption"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="233410" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/what-if-we-werent-afraid-to-tell-the-hard-truths-chris-chalk-on-playing-james-baldwin/feud_306_lock_121823-new-01-sub-05-copy/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FEUD_306_lock_121823.new_.01.Sub_.05-copy.jpg" data-orig-size="800,400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;FX\u2019s FEUD: Capote Vs. The Swans \&quot;The Secret Inner Lives of Swans\&quot; Airs Wednesday, February 21 at 10 p.m. ET\/PT -- Pictured:  Chris Chalk as James Baldwin. CR: FX&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1707431579&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;Copyright 2024, FX. All rights reserved.&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="FEUD_306_lock_121823.new.01.Sub.05 copy" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;FX’s FEUD: Capote Vs. The Swans &#8220;The Secret Inner Lives of Swans&#8221; Airs Wednesday, February 21 at 10 p.m. ET/PT &#8212; Pictured:  Chris Chalk as James Baldwin. CR: FX&lt;/p&gt;
